about.aboutContent:
According to the fast development of urban areas,unrenewable resources are becoming rare and very expensive, such as gasoline. As the consumption of gasoline rapidly increased, the environment is correspondingly getting worse, for instance, the continuous decline in air quality. To reduce consumption, the most effective action we can do in routine lives is to reduce consumption of transportation. Also, this is the easiest way that we can achieve sustainable urban development. Furthermore, urban parks are also very crucial in maintaining a good urban environment.

In this application, many transportation options are provided for finding parks in the city of Vancouver, but public transportation is strongly recommended. In addition information of Electronic Charging Stations are also available in this application. As the popularization of electronic vehicles, this supports people to have more convenient personal transportation that are generated by clean energy.

about.aboutContent:
Navigation:

Step1: Enter starting /destination address or simply clicking on the map (click these iconsfirst and then click on the map to choose locations).

Step2: Choose your transportation way and leave time.

Step3: Hit to get your routes.

 Adding stops between your destinations by clicking this icon.

Adding avoid areas by clicking on this icon and simply draw on the map, then your route will not include these areas.


Park Feature Filter

Clicking on the button beside the option, then parks with that facility will show on the map. These options can be used together.


Near by Parks/EV Charging Station/Bus Stops

Entering the address of your location or clicking this icon and then choose the location on the map. The search range can be adjusted by sliding the button. The search result will be presented on the map.


Query:

1.    Choose your interested options in the “Related layer.” 

2.    Click on the “Apply a search distance to selected features” to enable search distance.

3.    Click on the button on the bottom to obtain your search result, parks will with pinpoint on the map and also listed in the Results panel.

You can also use the drawing tool to search by clicking on this button:  


 Bookmark:

Zoom in to the location that you want to mark on the map, and then click this icon and edit the place name to save this place.
